00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
one I was talking about." It's fifty-eight degrees and clear

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
in Jefferson City, heading to eighty-two with afternoon storms likely.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Unbound starts today. Let's get into it. Starting with messages.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Katelyn is the big one. Around midnight she sent you

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.000
an Anthropic Greenhouse job posting link — she spotted a

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:16.000
specific role and wanted to flag it. She said the

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
qualifications list felt like it required more training or experience,

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.000
