00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.000
Pakistani mediators visited Tehran pushing both sides toward a second

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:04.000
round of talks. An A-P report says Washington and Tehran

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:08.000
